Package org.soulwing.prospecto.api

View and View Template API
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    View
    A view is a hierarchical organization of selected information from a model.
    View.Envelope
    An envelope for a view.
    View.Event
    An event for a view.
    ViewApplicator
    An applicator for a view.
    ViewContext
    A context used when evaluating view template with a model to produce a view.
    ViewEntity
    An abstract entity in a view.
    ViewReader
    A reader for a view.
    ViewReader.Source  
    ViewReaderFactory
    A factory that produces ViewReader objects.
    ViewTemplate
    A view template.
    ViewTemplate.Traversal
    A traversal for a ViewTemplate.
    ViewTemplateBuilder
    A builder for a ViewTemplate.
    ViewWriter
    A writer for a view.
    ViewWriter.Target  
    ViewWriterFactory
    A factory that produces ViewWriter instances.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UndefinedValue
    A value that is used to represent a missing or disallowed value during model update.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AccessMode
    An enumeration of access modes for model properties.
    AccessType
    An enumeration of access types for accessing model properties.
    View.Event.Type
    Event type
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ViewApplicatorException
    An exception thrown by a ViewApplicator.
    ViewException
    An exception thrown if the evaluation of a view fails.
    ViewInputException
    An exception thrown when processing the contents of a view as input in a ViewApplicator.
    ViewTemplateException
    An exception thrown when building a ViewTemplate.
